  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain proficiency with alchemist's supplies. During a long rest, you can use them to concoct an improvised @Item[MzlkOWQwMGY1OTJh]{Potion: Healing} by spending 1 hour of the long rest to tend to its simmering. Due to its improvised nature, it expires in 24 hours, and has no value in gold pieces.</p>\n<p>During this process, you can expend a 5th level spell to brew a @Item[wglwtsAJOil65n87]{Potion: Healing (Greater)} instead. The expended spell slot is regained when the long rest is completed as normal.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: This is not automated.&nbsp; A potion may be manually added to inventory and removed after expiration.&nbsp;</p>",
